<div class="attentionbox tip">
 If you hold the Option key while you click the Book panel's Print button, you'll get the Export dialogue!
</div>

<p>As you can see, working with a book file can save a lot of time compared to working with one long document. Theyâ€™ll help you keep things in sync between documents. You can also preflight and output really easily.</p>
